<tr><td align="center" bgcolor=pink>ラテン名</td></tr>
<tr><td align="center">musculus longissimus cervicis</td></tr>
<tr><td align="center" bgcolor=pink>英名</td></tr>
<tr><td align="center">Longissimus cervicis muscle</td></tr>
